{"tid":2061914,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[612感情台] 其實拍拖日日約真係好易心淡","createTime":"2020-06-12T17:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T04:35:30.000Z","uid":107157,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7b47b7bf7b369cd6da4e50e6716bca7d0de5f415","tid":2061914,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T17:41:28.000Z","msg":"214情人節，慶祝下，大家請日假出黎輕鬆下，已經好難忘好開心。<br />\n<br />\n去到白色情人節，元宵，元旦，七夕，中秋，兒童節，復活節，佛誕，端午節都要請假同你出黎慶祝，大佬你唔攰我都攰，慶祝得多會無feel架。你估下去到下年情人節，仲有幾多對情侶會出黎慶祝? 唔好問點解冇人出黎慶祝，原因我諗你自己都好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n任何野都有個度，心淡左就好難返返轉頭，死扯爛扯，最後都係分手收場。不如比啲時間，大家冷靜一排，話唔定可以重燃愛火呢？<br />\n<br />\n有啲野要忘記真係好難，但係要心淡真係可以好撚快。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911855fbb363dded4b1973e0d3a2297bda86c2b6","tid":2061914,"uid":303571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T17:54:38.000Z","msg":"對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我以為我哋無見一排你就會口淡"},{"pid":"c089703c1f819dc234d73db4383fb8e2a16f2274","tid":2061914,"uid":113093,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T18:00:15.000Z","msg":"佛誕 端午都要慶祝？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4783a612e4b1e58bc06cba33874be8a4dcc74b8","tid":2061914,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T01:27:02.000Z","msg":"612情人節"},{"pid":"ad5ce9d9dd42df503e75d3cecca05d02f20da744","tid":2061914,"uid":53815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T01:35:19.000Z","msg":"攰嘅咪休息下先，抖夠先出嚟慶祝，其他情侶冇心淡仲keep住出嚟慶祝，你應該佩服佢哋"},{"pid":"64516506b65cea9c627c079dc4777e8363b2be73","tid":2061914,"uid":47189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c089703c1f819dc234d73db4383fb8e2a16f2274","tid":2061914,"uid":113093,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T18:00:15.000Z","msg":"佛誕 端午都要慶祝？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmo